---
title: Louisiana Beef & Pork Rissoles with Roast Veggie Chunks, Smokey Aioli & Cucumber Salad
description: Rissoles are a crowd-pleasing dinner winner, but when you infuse them with melted Parmesan, they’re even harder to refuse! This
colourful plate also gets a serve of herby roasted veggie chunks and a family-friendly salad for a rainbow of delights.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
